				<wikidot:authorName>440 Hertz</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1249440</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I really really love it! I don't think I've ever seen cute genuine emotions expressed in such a flawless clinical tone. I feel embarrassed for not wanting to eat horrific mutant cell blobs shat out by a creepy chitinous critter, which is a slightly mind-boggling feeling to experience.</p> 
				 	]]>
